Class UserRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301f16t11.a2b.UserRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class UserRequest
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Model representing UserRequests. Contains distance, start, end locations, rider (who created the request), confirmed driver (if any), fare and other details.
